      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so excited to show you this absolute gem. It\u2019s been my total pride and joy, kept tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and pampered with hand-washes only. It looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single blemish or scratch anywhere! It drives like an absolute dream, and I\u2019m only letting it go to make room for a new project. You seriously have to see this beauty in person to believe how pristine it is. Drop me a message if you're interested\u2014I'd love to chat and get you behind the wheel!",
