    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine Carbon Black. This example features the legendary S54B32 inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and a fully serviced double-VANOS system. The rod bearings have been replaced as preventative maintenance, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure peak torsional rigidity. Power is managed via a precise ZF 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock. The suspension maintains factory-spec damping with no bushing play, providing the telepathic steering response these chassis are known for. Every aspect of the drivetrain and hydraulic systems is in peak operational order, presenting a rare opportunity for a mechanically-focused purist.",
